name: Langfield - Crunch Church
description:
4 track EP, 192kbps MP3s, looping video cover (hi-res files available to collectors) . 

 The debut EP from my electronic alter ego, Langfield. Taking in influences from New Order, Kraftwerk, Pye Corner Audio, Forest Swords, David Bowie, Boards of Canada, Radiohead, Steve Reich, Joy Division and many more. Eight years in the making, encompassing three house moves, two children and many, many burritos, Crunch Church is a love letter to the music that has shaped me. 

Crunch Church will also receive a traditional digital release later in the year.
